.serena/

# Build outputs (Gradle, etc.)
**/build/

# JS dependencies (defensive — main project is Java)
**/node_modules/

# Database dumps
**/dump/

# ArchUnit transient store at repo root only
# (snapshots in src/test/resources/archunit_store/ stay versioned)
/archunit_store/

# iCloud placeholders
**/*.icloud

# macOS Finder duplicates (Time Machine restore artefacts, drag-drop collisions)
**/* [0-9].*
**/* [0-9][0-9].*

# Documentation — keep only README.md, ignore other markdown files
*.md
!README.md
!**/README.md
